  "title": "KINDERGARTEN CARE CENTRE SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></u></p>\n<p>· Ensure smooth-running of daily operations at K-Care Centre inside a Primary School</p>\n<p>· Mentor and supervise team of K-Care Officers to ensure compliance to SOPs, safety and health standards</p>\n<p>· Take a class and conduct prescribed indoor/outdoor modular activities whenever needed</p>\n<p>· Maintain and build rapport with various stakeholders, especially school and parents</p>\n<p>· Handle administrative duties related to the K-Care Centre (e.g. fees collection, registration and withdrawals, administering of subsidy applications)</p>\n<p>· Handle emergencies and administer first aid, where applicable</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></u></p>\n<p>· Diploma in Early Childhood Care and Education – Teaching (DECCE-T)</p>\n<p>· At least 2 years of relevant experience in a preschool setting, preferably in a senior teacher/supervisory/leadership role</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>WORKING HOURS</strong></u></p>\n<p>During normal school term: 9.30am to 7pm (Mon to Fri)</p>\n<p>During school holiday: 9.5-hours shift between 7am to 7pm (Mon to Fri)</p>",
